ah-7-1255696">每位音乐家都拒绝了</a>一张有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timbaland">Timbaland</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/missy-elliott">Missy Elliott</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-8-1255721">死后Aaliyah专辑的报道</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">Drake</a>在2014年与已故歌手的谣言合作项目在她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-9-1257752">家人灰心</a>后被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-222-1231453">废除</a>。</p><p> 2021年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">周末</a>死后邀请了阿里亚（Aaliyah）参加联合单一的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-and-the-weeknd-to-appear-on-new-collaborative-single-poison-3119944">“毒药”</a> 。次年，Aaliyah的叔叔证实，一张名为Drake， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ne-yo">Ne-Yo</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future">Future</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyahs-uncle-confirms-posthumous-album-unstoppable-is-coming-this-month-3129661">的题为“不可阻挡”的专辑</a>将被发行，尽管它从未实现。</p><p> 2023年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-fans-petition-for-singer-to-be-inducted-into-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-3387179">球迷们请求将已故的明星引入摇滚名人堂</a>。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-launched-as-own-barbie-doll-on-what-would-have-been-her-own-46th-birthday-3829915">美泰（Mattel）在她的46岁生日时在她的纪念中推出了一个新的芭比娃娃，庆祝了已故的歌手</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/suge-knight-says-tupac-wanted-to-sign-aaliyah-3838427">苏格·奈特（Suge Knight）邮报（Post Suge Knight）说，图帕克（Tupac）想签下阿里亚（Aaliyah），</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
